<plot>A compilation by Burnet Hershey of newsreel shots of (the nine million) refugees of war-torn countries in Asia and Europe fleeing their native lands. The ending was studio shot and directed by Roy Mack with actors at a ship rail passing by process photography of the Statute of Liberty and singing a song written by Irving Caesar and Leo Edwards.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?579530</url></doc>
